{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.14"},"kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store"},{"type":"text","text":" type is now officially "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@MainActor"},{"type":"text","text":" isolated."}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","title":"Migrating to 1.14","modules":[{"name":"ComposableArchitecture"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigrationGuides"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"As the library prepares for Swift 6 we are in the process of updating the library’s APIs for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"sendability and isolation where appropriate, and doing so in a backwards compatible way. Prior","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to version 1.14 of the library the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store","isActive":true},{"text":" type has only ever been meant to be used on the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"main thread, but that contract was not enforced in any major way. If a store was interacted with","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"on a background thread a runtime warning would be emitted, but the compiler had no knowledge of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the type’s isolation.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"That now changes in 1.14 where "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store"},{"type":"text","text":" is now officially "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@MainActor"},{"type":"text","text":"-isolated. This has been"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"done in a way that should be 100% backwards compatible, and if you have problems please open a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"http:\/\/github.com\/pointfreeco\/swift-composable-architecture\/discussions"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"However, if you are using "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"strict","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" concurrency settings in your app, then there is one circumstance"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in which you may have a compilation error. If you are accessing the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"store"},{"type":"text","text":" in a view method or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property in Xcode <16, then you may have to mark that property as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@MainActor"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":[" struct FeatureView: View {","   let store: StoreOf<Feature>"," ","   var body: some View {","     \/\/ ...","   }"," ","+  @MainActor","   var title: some View {","     Text(store.name)","   }"," }"],"syntax":"diff"}]}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/migratingto1.14"]}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.19","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.18","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17.1","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/C